text: Maurice Jean Leonard Loustau-Lalanne is a Seychellois politician who presently serves as the Minister of Finance, Trade, Investment and Economic Planning. He was appointed by President Danny Faure on April 26, 2018. He was previously the Minister of Tourism in January 2016. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Seychelles politicians Category:Finance Ministers of Seychelles Category:Government ministers of Seychelles Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:United Seychelles Party politicians
